/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">他们备受期待的重返舞台</a>的消息，并确认明年夏天将<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-reunion-tour-uk-ireland-stadium-2025-liam-noel-gallagher-tickets-3787539">在英国和爱尔兰举行一系列大型体育场演出</a>。随后宣布了<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-extra-dates-to-north-american-2025-reunion-tour-due-to-phenomenal-demand-3799159">北美</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-2025-south-american-reunion-tour-dates-the-brothers-are-coming-buy-tickets-3809661">南美</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-add-more-dates-to-australia-2025-reunion-tour-3801693">澳大利亚</a>、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-south-korean-and-japan-dates-for-their-2025-reunion-tour-3814881">韩国和日本</a>的日期。</p><p>在得知他们将回归后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-respond-to-glastonbury-2025-rumours-and-the-chances-of-other-festivals-3788269">Oasis 排除了在 2025 年格拉斯顿伯里音乐节上进行头条表演的可能性</a>，并表示明年夏天他们不会出现在任何其他音乐节上。<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/could-oasis-return-to-knebworth-in-2026-3792709">利亚姆和诺埃尔也驳斥了 2026 年重返纳贝沃斯的传言</a>。</p><p>乐队宣布， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/cage-the-elephant">Cage The Elephant</a>将担任他们北美站的开场支持，而<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-confirm-richard-ashcroft-as-special-guest-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3804758">前 Verve 主唱兼独唱理查德·阿什克罗夫特 (Richard Ashcroft)</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/oasis-announce-cast-as-final-support-act-for-2025-uk-and-ireland-reunion-tour-3806934">卡斯特 (Cast)</a>将与曼彻斯特偶像一起参加他们在英国和爱尔兰的演出。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-now-denies-a-new-oasis-album-is-in-the-works-it-was-a-laugh-3813665">利亚姆最近反悔了他关于乐队目前正在录制一张新专辑的说法</a>，告诉歌迷“这很有趣”。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/liam-gallagher-wins-peta-award-for-adopting-homeless-dog-3820473">利亚姆·加拉格尔 (Liam Gallagher) 因收养无家可归的狗而荣获善待动物组织 (PETA) 奖的</a>帖子首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
