.com/news/music/my-chemical-romance-share-support-acts-for-upcoming-us-tour-3180364">大规模重聚巡演</a>，出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/when-we-were-young-2022-review-the-nostalgic-emo-fest-reigns-in-a-new-age-3338601">2022 年 When We Were Young 音乐节上</a>，并开始了 20 周年纪念巡演– 通过完整播放突破专辑《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/taking-back-sunday-announce-20th-anniversary-reissue-of-tell-all-your-friends-3194444">Tell All Your Friends</a> 》、《Louder Now》和《Where You Want To Be》来庆祝。</p><p>前<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-taking-back-sunday-perform-with-ex-guitarist-and-singer-fred-mascherino-for-the-first-time-in-17-years-3820425">吉他手兼歌手弗雷德·马斯切里诺 (Fred Mascherino) 与前吉他手兼歌手弗雷德·马斯切里诺 (Fred Mascherino) 合作的《Watch Take Back Sunday》节目于 17 年来首次</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
